## Quick Reference Log Sources & Table Mapping

| Log Source                    | Tool                        | Common Tables                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | Threat Hunting Value                                                                                    |
| ----------------------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Endpoint Logs                 | Defender for Endpoint (MDE) | `DeviceEvents`, `DeviceFileEvents`, `DeviceImageLoadEvents`, `DeviceInfo`, `DeviceLogonEvents`, `DeviceNetworkEvents`, `DeviceNetworkInfo`, `DeviceProcessEvents`, `DeviceRegistryEvents`, `DeviceFileCertificateInfo`, `DynamicEventCollection` | Detect malware execution, lateral movement, suspicious processes, persistence, and file manipulations   |
| Windows Security Events       | Sentinel                    | `SecurityEvent`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | Identify authentication anomalies, privilege escalations, and suspicious access attempts                |
| Entra ID Logs                 | Sentinel & Defender         | `SigninLogs`, `AuditLogs`, `IdentityLogonEvents`, `IdentityQueryEvents`, `IdentityDirectoryEvents`                                                                                                                                               | Detect suspicious logins, credential stuffing, account compromise, and abnormal administrative actions  |
| Office 365 Unified Audit Logs | Sentinel                    | `OfficeActivity`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | Detect unauthorized access, email rule manipulation, data exfiltration, and unusual file activity       |
| Cloud App Security (MCAS)     | Sentinel & Defender         | `CloudAppEvents`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | Identify shadow IT use, risky OAuth permissions, cloud data exfiltration, and unusual app behavior      |
| Email Events (Exchange)       | Sentinel                    | `EmailEvents`, `EmailAttachmentInfo`, `EmailPostDeliveryEvents`, `EmailUrlInfo`, `OfficeActivity`                                                                                                                                                | Detect phishing attempts, malicious attachments, suspicious URLs, and unusual email forwarding rules    |
| Firewall / VPN Logs (CEF)     | Sentinel                    | `CommonSecurityLog`                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | Monitor external connections, detect suspicious outbound/inbound traffic and anomalies in network flows |
| Linux & Network Devices       | Sentinel                    | `Syslog`, `CommonSecurityLog`                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | Identify anomalous network behavior, unauthorized device access, and unexpected configuration changes   |
| Security Alerts & Incidents   | Defender & Sentinel         | `SecurityAlert`, `SecurityIncident`, `AlertEvidence`                                                                                                                                                                                             | Correlate alerts, escalate incidents promptly, and investigate broader threat activity context          |
